  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment (W-AR-05 adversarial sample)",
  "description": "Synthetic V&V 40 credibility package for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. This package contains a deliberate W-AR-05 weakness: one validation result (vr-01) lacks a comparedAgainst link entirely, and a second validation result (vr-02) references a comparator dataset collected under dynamic cyclic loading conditions rather than the quasi-static compression-bending regime required by the declared COU. The comparator mismatch is an undercutting defeater (D3): the inference from experimental agreement to model credibility is undermined because the experimental conditions used for comparison do not correspond to the loading mode in which the model is intended to operate.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/nagaraja-f1717-compression-bending",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/nagaraja-fea-reproduces-f1717-static-cb",
