      "rationale": "Elastic moduli and Poisson ratios taken from ASTM F136 (Ti-6Al-4V) and ASTM A276 (316L SS). Screw geometry digitised from CMM measurements with tolerance ±0.01 mm. One-at-a-time sensitivity analysis across ±10% material property range yields maximum QoI variation of 3.1%. Input uncertainty adequately characterised."
