      "rationale": "N=11 constructs assembled from production-representative components (Lab 1 n=6, Lab 2 n=5). CMM measurements of screw outer diameter, thread pitch, and rod diameter confirm all specimens within ±0.02 mm of nominal. Inter-laboratory coefficient of variation for stiffness is 4.1%, indicating acceptable between-lab reproducibility. Sample representativeness is adequate."
    },
    {
