      "rationale": "Testing was conducted at a single compression-bending offset distance (50 mm) as specified by ASTM F1717. The COU does not require multi-configuration coverage, but the ASME V&V 40 required level for model risk 3 expects demonstration across at least two test conditions. Only one offset distance was evaluated, leaving this factor one gradation below required. This shortfall is documented and accepted by the credibility assessment team as a known limitation."
