      "rationale": "FEA model geometry updated from CMM measurements of each of the 11 physical constructs. Boundary conditions replicate ASTM F1717 fixture geometry (pin-pin, 50 mm offset). Applied displacement ramp rate (1 mm/min) is quasi-static; inertial effects negligible. Equivalency between simulation inputs and experimental conditions is well-established."
    },
