      "rationale": "Validation metric E/uval computed per ASME V&V 20 methodology incorporating experimental measurement uncertainty (load cell ±0.5%, displacement ±0.1 mm) and simulation numerical uncertainty (GCI-derived). All three QoIs satisfy both acceptance criteria. See validation results vr-01 and vr-02 for detailed numerical outcomes. Note: vr-02 uses a dynamically-loaded comparator dataset whose conditions do not match the quasi-static COU; the output comparison for vr-02 is therefore of limited inferential value despite satisfying the numerical threshold."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
